<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Esmer Web Ajans</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #0d0d0d;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
      padding: 15px 0;
      text-align: center;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: #00bcd4;
    }

    nav ul {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 25px;
      list-style: none;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    nav a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #00bcd4;
    }

    /* HERO SECTION */
    #anasayfa {
      height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000, #111 60%);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    #anasayfa h2 {
      font-size: 42px;
      color: #00bcd4;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      animation: fadeInDown 1s ease;
    }

    #anasayfa p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #ccc;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      animation: fadeInUp 1.2s ease;
    }

    .founder {
      color: #00bcd4;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 35px;
      animation: fadeInUp 1.4s ease;
    }

    .btn {
      background: #00bcd4;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      animation: fadeInUp 1.6s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #0096a3;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    @keyframes fadeInDown {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    /* DİĞER BÖLÜMLER */
    section {
      padding: 80px 20px;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: auto;
      text-align: center;
    }

    section h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      color: #00bcd4;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    section p {
      font-size: 17px;
      color: #ccc;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    /* İLETİŞİM */
    .contact-info a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 8px;
      color: #00bcd4;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .contact-info a:hover {
      color: #0096a3;
    }

    footer {
      background: #000;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Esmer Web Ajans</h1>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#anasayfa">Ana Sayfa</a></li>
        <li><a href="#hakkimizda">Hakkımızda</a></li>
        <li><a href="#hizmetler">Hizmetler</a></li>
        <li><a href="#iletisim">İletişim</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section id="anasayfa">
    <h2>Dijital Dünyada Gücünüzü Gösterin</h2>
    <p>Modern, yenilikçi ve etkileyici web çözümleriyle markanızı geleceğe taşıyoruz.  
       Profesyonel web tasarımı, SEO ve dijital pazarlama ile fark yaratın.</p>
    <p class="founder">Kurucu: <strong>Yılmaz Tekin</strong></p>
    <a href="#hizmetler" class="btn">Hizmetleri Gör</a>
  </section>

  <section id="hakkimizda">
    <h2>Hakk
